95
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:24,780
Lord Lou,

96
00:06:25,410 --> 00:06:26,700
did you forget

97
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:29,220
your promise?

98
00:06:30,570 --> 00:06:32,380
Someone wants to keep you alive.

99
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,410
I'm just following the order.

100
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:37,820
Your Highness,

101
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,660
I don't think you helped me
out of kindness.

102
00:06:42,130 --> 00:06:43,290
I'm helping you

103
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:45,540
because I want a deal.

104
00:06:46,450 --> 00:06:47,290
I've heard

105
