of Distortion Pill.

106
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:51,940
The drug is highly poisonous.

107
00:06:52,730 --> 00:06:53,940
Once made,

108
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:56,330
it'll bring disaster.

109
00:06:58,060 --> 00:07:00,130
His Majesty won't allow

110
00:07:00,130 --> 00:07:02,290
