111
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,730
even if some innocent people

112
00:07:04,730 --> 00:07:06,540
have to sacrifice themselves.

113
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:12,100
My Lord.

114
00:07:14,570 --> 00:07:15,730
What's going on?

115
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:19,570
Not a big deal.

116
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:21,060
Don't worry.

117
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:22,290
Father.

118
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:24,410
It's Lou Mingye and Lan Che's wedding.

119
00:07:24,610 --> 00:07:26,410
Why can't you choose another day?

120
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,980
He's the ingredient of Distortion Pill.

121
00:07:30,410 --> 00:07:32,700
I'm ordered to take him back.

122
00:07:37,450 --> 00:07:38,500
Let's go, Lord Lou.

123
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:47,130
Sorry.

124
00:07:50,100 --> 00:07:50,940
Wait a minute.

125
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:53,660
Your Highness.

126
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:56,290
You're doing it wrong.

127
00:07:58,130 --> 00:07:59,780
He's not the ingredient.

128
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:02,500
The person you're looking for

129
00:08:04,010 --> 00:08:04,850
is me.

130
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:11,300
Stop kidding.

131
00:08:11,550 --> 00:08:12,410
I'm not.

132
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:14,060
Lou Mingye.

133
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:16,330
I also have the purest yang energy.

134
00:08:17,170 --> 00:08:18,060
When we were kids,

135
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:20,780
