139
00:08:32,970 --> 00:08:35,170
Mingye hasn't received proper treatment.

140
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:36,970
Now he's dying.

141
00:08:37,970 --> 00:08:39,560
Only Qingyao's blood

142
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,530
can save him.

143
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:43,100
Mingye

144
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:45,170
is going to be the governor
of Liangzhou.

145
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:46,460
His safety

146
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:49,970
will affect the morale
of the entire Liangzhou army.

147
00:08:56,810 --> 00:08:57,650
Impossible.

148
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:01,170
We'll

149
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:02,700
figure it out.

150
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:04,860
Bring it.

151
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:08,340
The ingredient's blood is special.

152
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:10,580
The person whose blood

153
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:13,170
can activate the worm

154
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:15,020
is the real ingredient.

155
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:44,530
Lan Che,

156
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:45,780
please.

157
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:29,580
Maybe not.

158
00:10:30,290 --> 00:10:32,500
What if I leave you one day?

159
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:34,970
You'll need them

160
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,170
to marry someone else.

161
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:38,700
Marriage is not a game.

162
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,580
Have you made up your mind?

163
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:42,220
Lou Mingye.

164
00:10:43,610 --> 00:10:45,060
Don't make me regret this, okay?

165
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:52,140
Lan Che,

166
00:10:52,770 --> 00:10:53,820
come with me.

167
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:56,380
She can't.

168
00:10:58,850 --> 00:10:59,690
What did you say?

169
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:02,210
I said,

170
00:11:03,210 --> 00:11:04,460
she can't go with you.

171
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:05,780
Lou Mingye,

172
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:08,210
do you want to disobey the edict?

173
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:18,410
Don't you dare hurt my lord!

174
00:11:25,650 --> 00:11:26,750
Fang Tingge,

175
00:11:27,650 --> 00:11:30,020
I know you're
the best fighter in Liangzhou.

176
00:11:30,770 --> 00:11:32,380
But this is Changjing.

177
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,460
It doesn't work for me.

178
00:11:36,410 --> 00:11:37,610
Whoever hurts him,

179
00:11:38,650 --> 00:11:40,580
I'll cut their heads off.

180
00:11:45,650 --> 00:11:46,490
Your Highness,

181
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:50,060
I have to take Lan Che away today.

182
00:11:51,410 --> 00:11:52,250
After that,

183
00:11:53,260 --> 00:11:55,460
I'll ask His Majesty to punish me.

184
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:12,460
Let's take a break.

185
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:14,700
He can't find us right now.

186
00:12:22,170 --> 00:12:23,010
Lou Mingye.

187
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:27,090
Why did you promise him?

188
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:29,820
He helped me to catch Huo Feng,

189
00:12:31,290 --> 00:12:32,530
but I have to...

190
00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:36,410
Do you know Shanyin Pavilion in Donghai?

191
00:12:37,850 --> 00:12:39,340
When this is over.

192
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:40,970
You'll move there.

193
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:44,340
It's even worse than dying.

194
00:12:44,340 --> 00:12:45,650
So, I can't let you go.

195
00:12:49,410 --> 00:12:50,250
Lou Mingye.

196
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:53,210
I don't have much time left.

197
00:12:54,770 --> 00:12:56,460
You shouldn't have
disobeyed His Majesty.

198
00:12:57,610 --> 00:12:58,650
It's not worth it.

199
00:13:02,820 --> 00:13:03,700
Lan Che.

200
00:13:04,940 --> 00:13:06,140
I'm not going to let you lie.

201
00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:13,700
We haven't finished the wedding.

202
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:15,900
Three bows, right?

203
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,530
We have to finish it.

204
00:13:24,900 --> 00:13:26,410
Why don't we take the last bow

205
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:28,300
under the eye

206
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,090
of heaven and earth?

207
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:32,630
Okay.

208
00:13:39,210 --> 00:13:40,260
(In the presence)

209
00:13:41,290 --> 00:13:42,340
(of heaven and earth,)

210
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:45,260
(Lou Mingye and Lan Che)

211
00:13:47,170 --> 00:13:48,610
(are married to each other.)

212
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:52,770
(Stay with each other)

213
00:13:55,170 --> 00:13:56,700
(till death do us part.)

214
00:13:58,210 --> 00:13:59,900
(Love each other when we're alive)

215
00:14:00,700 --> 00:14:02,380
(and keep each other in mind
after death.)

216
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:46,740
