Help!

217
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:47,650
Let me out!

218
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:49,410
Are you crazy?

219
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:50,730
Don't you know me?

220
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:53,540
Help!

221
00:14:53,650 --> 00:14:54,650
Let me out!

222
00:14:55,650 --> 00:14:56,900
Are you crazy?

223
00:15:01,610 --> 00:15:02,450
It's you.

224
00:15:07,610 --> 00:15:09,170
My Lord, please calm down.

225
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:10,700
I have no choice.

226
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:14,500
You're good at fighting.

227
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:16,900
Only in this way can we control you.

228
00:15:18,290 --> 00:15:19,170
I'm so sorry.

229
00:15:31,170 --> 00:15:32,210
What are you thinking?

230
00:15:35,530 --> 00:15:37,340
I'm thinking about our future.

231
00:15:47,090 --> 00:15:48,380
Look at us.

232
00:15:48,770 --> 00:15:50,170
Our outfits are too noticeable.

233
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:52,090
There's a farmer.

234
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:54,610
Buy some common clothes

235
00:15:55,210 --> 00:15:56,170
for us, okay?

236
00:15:59,210 --> 00:16:00,050
Okay.

237
00:16:00,580 --> 00:16:01,820
Wait here.

238
00:16:03,020 --> 00:16:03,860
Okay.

239
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:38,300
Your Highness,

240
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,650
Lan Che wants to see you.

241
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:43,660
Bring her in.

242
00:16:43,730 --> 00:16:44,570
Aye.

243
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:53,900
Lou Mingye is disobedient,

244
00:16:55,770 --> 00:16:57,410
but you're smart.

245
00:16:59,940 --> 00:17:00,780
Your Highness,

246
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:02,660
can you

247
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:04,460
do me a favor?

248
00:17:05,890 --> 00:17:06,730
Tell me.

249
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:10,250
My master and friends
have nothing to do with this.

250
00:17:10,580 --> 00:17:12,060
Can you please release them?

251
00:17:13,650 --> 00:17:15,530
They're useless.

252
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:18,250
I never wanted to give them a hard time.

253
00:17:18,940 --> 00:17:19,890
As for Lou Mingye...

254
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:23,170
Can you please forgive him?

255
00:17:27,410 --> 00:17:29,580
If he behaves himself...

256
00:17:34,010 --> 00:17:35,700
I'll have mercy on him.

257
00:17:37,860 --> 00:17:39,250
However,

258
00:17:39,890 --> 00:17:41,890
it's all up to you.

259
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:43,420
Your Highness,

260
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:46,410
since you're so generous,

261
00:17:47,940 --> 00:17:48,780
then I'll

262
00:17:50,130 --> 00:17:51,620
