263
00:17:52,290 --> 00:17:53,820
and go to Shanyin Pavilion.

264
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:56,620
Who told you about

265
00:17:57,820 --> 00:17:59,530
Shanyin Pavilion?

266
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:09,530
Lord Lou.

267
00:18:10,250 --> 00:18:11,090
Your Highness,

268
00:18:11,530 --> 00:18:12,740
