272
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:24,770
I can't let her die alone.

273
00:18:28,290 --> 00:18:29,530
Please fulfill my wish.

274
00:18:37,490 --> 00:18:39,940
As you once worked with my son,

275
00:18:40,740 --> 00:18:42,890
I'll have mercy this time,

276
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:45,650
but don't go too far.

277
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:49,970
Your Highness...

278
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,180
Walk him out.

279
00:18:54,530 --> 00:18:55,580
My Lord, please.

280
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,940
Which troop are you from?

281
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:34,490
My Lord, look.

282
00:19:36,490 --> 00:19:37,980
It's said the burned soldiers

283
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:39,890
went mad before they died.

284
00:19:39,890 --> 00:19:41,690
They were so strong
and would attack anyone.

285
00:19:45,340 --> 00:19:47,770
That's the symptom of being poisoned
by both Carefree Powder

286
00:19:48,010 --> 00:19:49,220
and Oblivion Drug.

287
00:19:50,650 --> 00:19:52,010
Huanxi told me

288
00:19:52,460 --> 00:19:53,890
when they were making the drug,

289
00:19:54,290 --> 00:19:56,940
they found if one only takes
one of the drugs,

290
00:19:57,170 --> 00:19:58,700
he'll be extremely strong,

291
00:19:58,940 --> 00:20:00,650
but it'll only last for three days.

292
00:20:00,860 --> 00:20:03,340
After that, he'll die of
excessive bleeding.

